race.comment: HEY PRESTO (1) failed to come into contention last start after losing her position early at The Meadows, but prior to that won by half a length at Warragul (26.20) beating Aston Eleni in a Grade 5 on September 5. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Should bounce back. WISE ABALONE (2) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 5 length third (26.49) over 460m at Warragul. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Expected to be in the finish again. AKINA JACK (7) was below best last time but prior to that was narrowly beaten when fourth (29.18) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Can feature with the right run. BETTY'S GARDEN (4) cannot be left out after placing in impressive time last start.
